<br>
The original reason that Necros <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>were</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> such great soloers was primarily because they were such crappy additions to groups. Their entire spell line was self-serving and thus, they were rewarded with great soloing power.<br>
<br>
Nowadays, this relationship no longer seems true, where is it possible for one class to be nearly essential for groups but can also be the best soloers at will.<br>
